task.summary: First commit of project. Added virtual environment and initial bot code.
Added virtual environment and initial bot code.
Fixed bittrex.py file in virtual environment. Once you set up project in pycharm it should be able to run smoothly.
Added: local authentication with sqllite. Structure of application is easier to follow. Removed: Firebase authentication.
Added auth module controller and model. Also added 404 page.
Added the bit bot tester '/trade' to access it.
Added current wallet status and current coin price based on selected option in dropdown.
Start bot implementation. Bot returns last ask price and the highest and lowest bollinger band % for a specific market. Data is requested every 5 seconds.
Fixed root index page. Added stop bot functionality.
